+### Schema Lifecycle
+
+| Use case | Status | Notes |
+|----------|--------|-------|
+| Declare a new book at startup | ✅ Kit `books` contribution | Declarative; reconciliation is additive only |
+| Add an index to an existing book | ✅ Kit `books` contribution | Additive; existing data preserved |
